{"tid":297093,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒︰曼聯將簽入史奈達","createTime":"2017-06-25T07:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T16:05:30.000Z","uid":56680,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa31077e351b5c3d00b76770fc489e97c4cf7da","tid":297093,"uid":56680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒報道，曼聯會在轉會窗關閉前簽入加拉塔沙雷球星史奈達。據《每日快報》報道，去年夏天未能將荷蘭國腳史奈達羅致的紅魔主帥摩連奴，在冬季轉會窗關閉前將會獲得這名32歲球星加盟，而原本亦對史奈達有興趣的祖雲達斯，已將目標轉移至多蒙特的丹比利。到底史奈達是否會到前國米恩師摩連奴麾下作賽，很快便有分曉。"},{"pid":"1381860d83ea08d51c4db23d05b985bf0ea55c6a","tid":297093,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"仲黎？！"},{"pid":"5c4c0149ae0b60d56b9e6aa720d1ba55165e3d47","tid":297093,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc383bd67ce30942cf79b6e1cec8a075d0503bf","tid":297093,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"名宿"},{"pid":"90503a80f49750e0a8a32525d3d1776619f12374","tid":297093,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68e37ef309d3cf873f8e312737dd76598438c26","tid":297093,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"22歲傳到32歲都未買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f08a051112a7210794379ba19eed7b1b57d90f","tid":